@realmoney I have one thought over the weekend. To me, too many investors look backwards in the rear view mirror or what is immediately in front of us... and not into the future. Long dated assets, like equities, discount years (10-20) in advance. Discounted dividend models,

using 15 years (or 60 months), are little impacted by the next 3-4 quarters (3.5/60 weighting). Enjoy the weekend. Be safe. @tomkeene @jimcramer @SquawkCNBC @cnbcfastmoney @riskreversal @andrewrsorkin @beckyquick @carlquintanilla @michaelsantoli
